summary: CONSUMER STATES THAT TRUNK LID DOES NOT STAY UP WHEN OPENED.  WHEN TRUNK IS OPENED LID FALLS BACK DOWN.  CONSUMER AND OTHER FAMILY MEMBERS HAVE BEEN HIT IN THE HEAD SEVERAL TIMES WHILE LOADING AND UNLOADING ITEMS FROM THE TRUNK.  CONSUMER CONTACTED MANUFACTURER WHO ADVISED THAT TRUNK IS OPERATING WITHIN SPECIFICATIONS. TS
